NK040(thi)040:1: // mkha' 'gro sde lnga'i bskang ba'i dbu phyogs lags so //
NK040(thi)040:2: na mo gu ru badz+ra d+aak+ki ni ye /
NK040(thi)040:3: bla ma rdo rje mkha' 'gro'i zhabs la gus par phyag 'tshal lo //
NK040(thi)040:4: rnal 'byor dam tshig dang sdom pa'i chags nyams gso ba dang /
NK040(thi)040:5: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro'i thugs dam bskang zhing
NK040(thi)040:6: mchog dang thun mong gis dngos grub bde legs su
NK040(thi)040:8: dur khrod la sogs pa'i gnas khyad par can du dkon mchog gsum gyis rten bkram /
NK040(thi)040:9: mkha' 'gro sde lnga'i rdul tshon nam /
NK040(thi)040:11: mchod pa'i tshogs dang gtor ma 'dod yon phun sum tshogs pas brgyan pa lnga /
NK040(thi)040:12: nang mchod dang rdo rje dril bu la sogs pa rol mo'i bye brag rnams dang /
NK040(thi)040:13: gzhan yang mchod pa'i rdzas ci 'byor pa dang /
NK040(thi)040:14: tshogs gtor la sogs bshams la dge 'dun la sogs 'tshogs nas gdan la 'khod de /
NK040(thi)040:15: sngon 'gro'i gtor ma nas tshogs kyi gzhung bsrang ste /
NK040(thi)040:17: tshogs kyis 'khor los dpa' bo dpa' mo rnal 'byor pa rnams kyis 'tsho bar byas la /
NK040(thi)040:18: dmigs pas rgyas pa dkyil 'khor gdab cing /
NK040(thi)040:19: snyan pa'i dbyangs dang bcas pas 'di skad do //
NK040(thi)040:21: sra brten rgya khyon ches che bas //
NK040(thi)040:22: rdo rje'i sa gzhi rwa gur dang //
NK040(thi)040:23: bla re bskal pa'i me ri'i bskor //
NK040(thi)040:24: dbus su chos 'byus rgya che bar //
NK040(thi)040:25: rlung me chu sa ri rab steng //
NK040(thi)040:26: steng du gzhal med khang chen po //
NK040(thi)040:27: gru bzhi sgo bzhi rta bab bzhi //
NK040(thi)040:28: rgyan rnams kun gyis rnam par spras //
NK040(thi)040:29: 'jig rten khams ni ma lus pas //
NK040(thi)040:31: dur khrod chen po brgyad dang bcas //
NK040(thi)040:32: dbus sngo shar dkar lho ser zhing //
NK040(thi)040:33: nub dmar byang ljang dbus su ni //
NK040(thi)040:34: sna tshogs pad+ma'i lte ba dang //
NK040(thi)040:35: 'dab ma rnams su nyi ma la //
NK040(thi)040:36: bdag med stong pa'i ro'i gdan //
NK040(thi)040:37: phyi nang kun tu lha rdzas las //
NK040(thi)040:38: grub pa'i kun bzang mchod pa'i sprin //
NK040(thi)040:39: dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i gtor chen las //
NK040(thi)040:40: 'dod yon phun sum tshogs pa'i brgyan //
NK040(thi)040:41: lha rdzas rnams kyi yid 'phrog pas //
NK040(thi)040:42: bla na med pa'i gnas mchog 'dir //
NK040(thi)040:43: ces pas gnas dang mchod rdzas gsal gdab la /
NK040(thi)040:44: rol mo'i sgra dang bcas pa spyan 'dren par bya ste /
NK040(thi)040:46: 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang nas //
NK040(thi)040:47: rdo rje 'chang dbang rtsa ba'i bla ma dang //
NK040(thi)040:48: gzhan yang chos kyi 'brel ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK040(thi)040:49: brgyud pa'i bla ma grub thob pho mo rnams //
NK040(thi)040:50: brtse ba'i thugs rje bdag la nyer dgongs ste //
NK040(thi)040:51: bla na med pa'i gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK040(thi)040:53: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK040(thi)040:54: chos sku spros bral smra bsam las 'das zhing //
NK040(thi)040:55: ye shes sgyu ma'i gzugs sku'i gzhan don mdzad //
NK040(thi)040:56: mkha' 'gro'i tshogs rnams brtse bas gnas 'dir gshegs //
NK040(thi)040:58: mkha' dbyings rnam dag klong yang dkyil 'khor nas //
NK040(thi)040:59: sangs rgyas bstan 'dzin skyong ba dang //
NK040(thi)040:60: bstan la gnod byed bsgral ba dam bcas pas //
NK040(thi)040:61: phyi nang chos skyong tshogs rnams gnas 'dir gshegs //
NK040(thi)040:63: sangs rgyas bstan la dad pa brten gyur cig /
NK040(thi)040:64: bstan 'dzin thams cad chos bzhin skyong ba dang //
NK040(thi)040:65: 'dod don ma lus bsgrub pa'i mthu rtsal can //
NK040(thi)040:66: dregs pa can rnams gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK040(thi)040:67: ma h+aa gu ru d+he wa d+aak+ki ni sarba d+harma
NK040(thi)040:68: pa la sa pa ri wa ra e h+ya hi
NK040(thi)040:70: pad+ma ka ma la ye stam /
NK040(thi)040:72: gdan dang gzhal yas phul la phyi yi mchod pas thugs dam bskang ba ni /
NK040(thi)040:74: phyi yi mchod pa 'bul ba ni //
NK040(thi)040:75: thod pa mtshan ldan ka pa la //
NK040(thi)040:76: rak+ta'i mchod yon zhabs bsil dang //
NK040(thi)040:77: dbang po lnga'i me tog dang //
NK040(thi)040:78: sha chen lang ling bdug spos dang //
NK040(thi)040:79: zhun chen sbar ba'i snang gsal dang //
NK040(thi)040:80: rdo rje rang byung dri chab dang //
NK040(thi)040:81: sha khrag rus pa las byung bas //
NK040(thi)040:82: ro brgya ldan pa'i zhal zas dang //
NK040(thi)040:83: dam sri pho mo bsgral ba yi //
NK040(thi)040:84: dung chen gling bu thod lnga dang //
NK040(thi)040:85: spyi bor sprad pa'i cang til dang //
NK040(thi)040:86: mkha' 'gro'i tshogs rnams dbang bsdud phyir //
NK040(thi)040:87: gsang ba'i rnge'u chung la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)040:88: sna tshogs rol mo'i sgra dbyangs 'di //
NK040(thi)040:89: bla ma brgyud pa bcas la 'bul //
NK040(thi)040:90: sku gsung thugs mchog mnyes gyur cig /
NK040(thi)040:91: rnal 'byor lam mchog bsgrub pa yi //
NK040(thi)040:92: rtsa ba dang ni yan lag gis //
NK040(thi)040:93: dam tshig chags nyams gyur pa rnams //
NK040(thi)040:94: bskang gyur dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK040(thi)040:95: rgyu sbyor yon gyi bdag po yi //
NK040(thi)040:96: tshe bsring dpal bskyed bsam pa bsgrub //
NK040(thi)040:97: mi mthun rkyen dang bar chad sel //
NK040(thi)040:100: dkyil 'khor chen po'i dbus bzhugs pa'i //
NK040(thi)040:101: zhe sdang rnam shes rnam dag cing //
NK040(thi)040:102: chos dbyings ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK040(thi)040:103: rang bzhin 'gyur med sku mdog sngo //
NK040(thi)040:104: bde stong zung 'jug phyag gnyis ma //
NK040(thi)040:105: rgyu drug gcod pa'i gri gug dang //
NK040(thi)040:106: bdud bzhi'i khrag bkang thod pa bsnams //
NK040(thi)040:107: bcom ldan rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma //
NK040(thi)040:109: sku gsung thugs mchog mnyes gang bzhin 'gres /
NK040(thi)040:111: shar gyi phyogs na bzhugs pa yi //
NK040(thi)040:112: gti mug gzugs phung rnam dag pa //
NK040(thi)040:113: me long ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK040(thi)040:114: nad gdon zhi mdzad sku mdog dkar //
NK040(thi)040:115: phyag gnyis gri gug thod pa 'brel //
NK040(thi)040:116: bcom ldan sangs rgyas mkha'i 'gro ma //
NK040(thi)040:120: lho yi phyogs nas bzhugs pa yi //
NK040(thi)040:121: nga rgyal tshor phung rnam dag cing //
NK040(thi)040:122: mnyam nyid ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK040(thi)040:123: tshe dpal rgyas mdzad sku mdog ser //
NK040(thi)040:124: phyag gnyis gri gug thod pa 'brel //
NK040(thi)040:125: bcom ldan rin chen mkha' 'gro ma //
NK040(thi)040:127: sku gsung thugs mchog mnyes gyur cig /
NK040(thi)040:128: rnal 'byor lam mchog bsgrub pa yi //
NK040(thi)040:129: rtsa ba dang ni yan lag gis //
NK040(thi)040:130: dam tshig chags nyams gyur pa kun //
NK040(thi)040:131: bskang gyur dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK040(thi)040:132: rgyu 'byor yon gyi bdag po yi //
NK040(thi)040:133: tshe bsring dpal bskyed bsam pa bsgrub //
NK040(thi)040:134: me mthun rkyen dang bar chad sel //
NK040(thi)040:137: nub kyi phyogs nas bzhugs pa yis //
NK040(thi)040:139: sor rtog ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK040(thi)040:140: lha mi dbang bsdud sku mdog dmar //
NK040(thi)040:141: phyag gnyis gri gug thod pa 'brel //
NK040(thi)040:146: byang gi phyogs na bzhugs pa yi //
NK040(thi)040:147: phrag dog 'du shes rnam dag cing //
NK040(thi)040:148: bya grub ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK040(thi)040:149: dgra bgegs sgrol mdzad sku mdog ljang //
NK040(thi)040:150: phyag gnyis gri gug thod pa 'brel //
NK040(thi)040:151: bcom ldan las kyi mkha' 'gro ma //
NK040(thi)040:152: 'khor dang bcas la sku mdog thugs mchog sogs /
NK040(thi)040:154: dus gsum mkhyen cing khams gsum la //
NK040(thi)040:155: gzigs pa spyan gsum g.yon du bsgyur //
NK040(thi)040:156: ye shes mkha' 'gro sde lnga yis //
NK040(thi)040:157: bskang ngo bskal pa'i thugs dam bskang //
NK040(thi)040:159: mtha' gnyis mi gnas brkyang bskum bzhugs //
NK040(thi)040:160: ye shes mkha' 'gro sde lnga yi //
NK040(thi)040:161: bskang ngo bskal sku gsung thugs yon phrin las mtshon //
NK040(thi)040:162: thabs kyi rang bzhin kha t+w+aam kha //
NK040(thi)040:163: shes rab mkha' 'gro sde lnga yi //
NK040(thi)040:164: bskang ngo bskal rus pa'i 'khor lo rdo rje sems //
NK040(thi)040:165: rna ba'i rgyan cha 'od dpag med //
NK040(thi)040:166: mgul gyi phreng ba rin chen 'byung //
NK040(thi)040:167: gdub bu rnam par snang mdzad dang //
NK040(thi)040:168: sku reg don yod grub pa ste //
NK040(thi)040:169: thabs shes pha rol phyin lnga yi //
NK040(thi)040:170: shes rab pha rol phyin pa'i thugs dam bskang //
NK040(thi)040:171: bskang ngo bskal pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa lnga dag pas //
NK040(thi)040:172: thod skam lnga yi dpa' bo yi //
NK040(thi)040:173: dbu la rab tu mdzes par brgyan //
NK040(thi)040:174: bskang ngo bskal pa'i a li ka li rnam dag pa'i //
NK040(thi)040:175: thod rlon 'phreng ba lnga bcu'i do shal dang //
NK040(thi)040:176: thabs shes zung 'jug tshang skud dang //
NK040(thi)040:177: dung chen phreng ba dpa' bo yi //
NK040(thi)040:178: rab tu mdzes par brgyan pa yi //
NK040(thi)040:179: bskang ngo bskal pa'i sgrib pa'i tshang tshing kun bsreg cing //
NK040(thi)040:182: ye shes mkha' 'gro sde lnga yi //
NK040(thi)040:184: gzhan yang thugs dam bskang ba'i rdzas //
NK040(thi)040:185: 'jig rten khams ni ci snyed bar //
NK040(thi)040:186: kha dog dbyibs legs gzugs rnams dang //
NK040(thi)040:187: zin dang ma zin sgra snyan dang //
NK040(thi)040:188: yid la bsam pa'i dri mchog dang //
NK040(thi)040:189: ro brgya ldan pa'i zhal zas dang //
NK040(thi)040:191: ri rab gling bzhi gling phran dang //
NK040(thi)040:192: ri bdun rol pa'i mtsho bdun dang //
NK040(thi)040:193: nyi ma zla ba'i snang gsal dang //
NK040(thi)040:194: rnam rgyal khang bzang blta na sdug /
NK040(thi)040:195: 'dod khams gzugs khams gzugs med khams //
NK040(thi)040:196: mchod par 'os pa ci snyed pas //
NK040(thi)040:197: ye shes mkha' 'gro sde lnga yi //
NK040(thi)040:198: bskang ngo bskal pa'i thugs dam bskang //
NK040(thi)040:199: de nas nang gi mchod pas thugs dam bskang ba ni /
NK040(thi)040:201: gzhan yang thugs dam bskang ba'i rdzas //
NK040(thi)040:202: 'bru gsum las grub thod sgyed gsum //
NK040(thi)040:203: steng du ye shes k+aa pa la //
NK040(thi)040:204: sha lnga bdud rtsi ye shes lnga //
NK040(thi)040:205: me rlung sbyor ba'i bzhus bskul bas //
NK040(thi)040:208: ye shes lnga'i kha dog dri //
NK040(thi)040:209: reg bya nus pa phun sum tshogs //
NK040(thi)040:210: nang gi mchod pa rgya chen 'di //
NK040(thi)040:211: bla ma brgyud pa bcas la 'bul //
NK040(thi)040:212: yi dam mkha' 'gro sde lnga dang //
NK040(thi)040:213: rgyud sde bzhi yi lha tshogs dang //
NK040(thi)040:214: phyogs bcu'i dus gsum bzhugs pa yi //
NK040(thi)040:215: rgyal ba sras dang bcas la 'bul //
NK040(thi)040:216: sku gsung thugs mchog mnyes gyur cig /
NK040(thi)040:217: rnal 'byor lam mchog sgrub pa yi //
NK040(thi)040:218: rtsa ba dang ni yan lag gis //
NK040(thi)040:219: dam tshig chag nyams gyur pa kun //
NK040(thi)040:220: bskang gyur dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK040(thi)040:221: rgyu sbyor yon gyi bdag po yi //
NK040(thi)040:222: tshe bsring dpal bskyed bsam pa bsgrub //
NK040(thi)040:223: mi mthun rkyen dang bar chad sel //
NK040(thi)040:226: gzhan yang thugs dam bskang ba ni //
NK040(thi)040:227: rdo rje 'chang gis spyan snga ru //
NK040(thi)040:228: bstan pa srung bar khas blangs pa //
NK040(thi)040:229: ye shes mgon po ci snyed pa //
NK040(thi)040:230: ma cig lha mo'i tshogs rnams dang //
NK040(thi)040:231: nag po stong dang sha za 'bum //
NK040(thi)040:232: ma mo bye ba'i tshogs dang bcas //
NK040(thi)040:233: sprul pa yang sprul bcas la 'bul //
NK040(thi)040:235: de nas srung ma'i thugs dam bskang ba ni /
NK040(thi)040:237: gzhan yang thugs dam bskang ba ni //
NK040(thi)040:238: ma cig lab sgron spyan snga ru //
NK040(thi)040:239: bstan pa srung bar zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK040(thi)040:240: myur mdzad mgon po phyag drug pa //
NK040(thi)040:241: 'dod khams dbang phyug re ma ti //
NK040(thi)040:242: k+she ta pa la gnod sbyin bzhi //
NK040(thi)040:243: gtsang ris dpal mgon bdun cu gnyis //
NK040(thi)040:244: zhi byed srung ma a g+ho ra //
NK040(thi)040:245: bzlog byed ma dang nor rgyun ma //
NK040(thi)040:246: gcod kyi bka' srung dur khrod bdag /
NK040(thi)040:247: mtshan mo sgra sgrog spyang zhon ma //
NK040(thi)040:248: stag zhon ma dang 'phar zhon ma //
NK040(thi)040:249: sham po'i gza' bdud mgo dgu dang //
NK040(thi)040:250: thog gi bu yug gdong mo bzhi //
NK040(thi)040:251: gza' brgyad zangs ri 'khyil ba sogs //
NK040(thi)040:252: sprul 'khor bcas pa'i thugs dam bskang //
NK040(thi)040:255: gzhan yang thugs dam bskang ba ni //
NK040(thi)040:256: zhang blon rdo rje bdud 'dul dang //
NK040(thi)040:257: yum gnyis mched brgyad gnod sbyin khri //
NK040(thi)040:258: 'brog gnas lnga dang rgyal chen bzhi //
NK040(thi)040:259: thang lha 'o de gung rgyal dang //
NK040(thi)040:260: mkha' ri lcam dral yar lha sham //
NK040(thi)040:261: brtan ma bcu gnyis sman phran 'bum //
NK040(thi)040:262: klu rgyal drag po zla skyong sogs //
NK040(thi)040:263: zab mo gcod kyi bstan srung dang //
NK040(thi)040:264: sa phyogs 'di yi gzhi bdag sogs //
NK040(thi)040:265: chos la dga' ba kun la 'bul //
NK040(thi)040:267: de nas gtor ma'i thugs dam bskang ba ni /
NK040(thi)040:269: gzhan yang thugs dam bskang ba ni //
NK040(thi)040:270: sangs rgyas bstan la gnod byed pa //
NK040(thi)040:271: dgra bgegs log 'dren bsgral ba yis //
NK040(thi)040:272: gtor chen dmar gyi brgyan pa dang //
NK040(thi)040:273: sman rag chang dang phud kyis bran //
NK040(thi)040:274: bsang sbyang 'dod yon phun sum tshogs //
NK040(thi)040:275: kha dog dri ro nus ldan zhing //
NK040(thi)040:276: bla na med pa'i mchod pa 'di //
NK040(thi)040:277: bla ma brgyud par bcas la 'bul //
NK040(thi)040:279: rgyud sde bzhi yi lha la 'bul //
NK040(thi)040:280: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba rnams la 'bul //
NK040(thi)040:281: phyi nang dge 'dun rnams la 'jig rten 'das dang ma 'das pa //
NK040(thi)040:282: bsrung ma dam can rnams la skyong ma bstan ma shug 'gro dang //
NK040(thi)040:283: dregs pa can gyis tshogs la 'bul //
NK040(thi)040:286: gnam sa'i rgyan la sogs pas mchod cing thugs dam bskang ba ni /
NK040(thi)040:288: gzhan yang thugs dam bskang ba ni //
NK040(thi)040:289: sangs rgyas bstan la gnod byed pa'i //
NK040(thi)040:290: dgra dang bgegs rnams bsgral ba yi //
NK040(thi)040:291: king rus phreng ba sa gzhi'i brgyan //
NK040(thi)040:292: tsit+ta tsa lag tshong ba dang //
NK040(thi)040:293: rgyu rlon lda ldi bar snang brgyan //
NK040(thi)040:294: g.yang gzhi bla re nam mkha'i rgyan //
NK040(thi)040:295: rgyan cha yid 'ong sna tshogs dang //
NK040(thi)040:296: khrag zhag rgya mtsho 'khyil pa dang /
NK040(thi)040:297: sha rigs sna tshogs ri ltar spungs //
NK040(thi)040:298: klad pa nang rol sna tshogs dang //
NK040(thi)040:299: drod dang dri bsung ma yal ba //
NK040(thi)040:300: dpa' bo mkha' 'gro mnyes byed pa //
NK040(thi)040:301: bla na med pa'i mchod pa 'di //
NK040(thi)040:302: bla ma brgyud pa bcas la 'bul //
NK040(thi)040:304: rgyud sde bzhi yi lha la 'bul //
NK040(thi)040:305: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba rnams la 'bul //
NK040(thi)040:306: phyi nang dge 'dun rnams la 'jig rten 'das dang ma 'das pa //
NK040(thi)040:307: srung ma dam can rnams la 'bul //
NK040(thi)040:308: skyong ma bstan ma shug 'gro dang //
NK040(thi)040:309: dregs pa can gyi tshogs la 'bul //
NK040(thi)040:311: de nas bskang rdzas sna tshogs kyi thugs dam bskang ba ni /
NK040(thi)040:313: gzhan yang thugs dam bskang ba'i rdzas //
NK040(thi)040:314: mkha' lding la sogs 'dab chags dang //
NK040(thi)040:315: seng ge stag gzig khyi la sogs //
NK040(thi)040:316: gcan gzan ci snyed yod pa dang //
NK040(thi)040:317: cang shes rta mchog la sogs pa //
NK040(thi)040:318: myur 'gyogs rlung gi gshog pa can //
NK040(thi)040:319: g.yag nag zhub can lug nag sogs //
NK040(thi)040:320: rab mdzes yid 'ong du ma yis //
NK040(thi)040:321: sna tshogs brgyan gyis brgyan pa dang //
NK040(thi)040:322: rin chen sna lnga'i phye ma yi //
NK040(thi)040:323: zhal zas tshogs kyi mchod pa dang //
NK040(thi)040:324: drag po'i bshos bu zur gsum dang //
NK040(thi)040:325: sna tshogs dar gyi lhab lhub dang //
NK040(thi)040:326: mkha' lding nag po gser mig dang //
NK040(thi)040:328: tsa ra rog po mkhal dkar dang //
NK040(thi)040:329: gsang ba'i rgyal mtshan 'phan gdug dang //
NK040(thi)040:330: bya mo nag mo la sogs dang //
NK040(thi)040:331: rlung gi khyer ba'i shing lo dang //
NK040(thi)040:332: gsang ba'i sha khrag la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)040:334: ci snyed yod pa thams cad dang //
NK040(thi)040:335: bla ma brgyud pa bcas la 'bul //
NK040(thi)040:336: thugs dam dgongs pa bskang gyur cig /
NK040(thi)040:337: rnal 'byor bdag gis nyams chags kun //
NK040(thi)040:338: bskang gyur dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK040(thi)040:339: gzhan yang thugs dam bskang ba ni //
NK040(thi)040:340: yi dam dkyil 'khor lha tshogs dang //
NK040(thi)040:341: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sras bcas dang //
NK040(thi)040:342: phyi dang nang gi srung ma dang //
NK040(thi)040:343: bstan la dga' ba'i lha klu yi //
NK040(thi)040:344: thugs dam dgongs pa bskang gyur nas //
NK040(thi)040:345: rnal 'byor bdag gi nyams chag kun //
NK040(thi)040:346: bskang gyur dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK040(thi)040:347: sku gsung thugs mchog mnyes gyur cig /
NK040(thi)040:348: rnal 'byor lam mchog bsgrub pa yis //
NK040(thi)040:349: rtsa ba dang ni yan lag gis //
NK040(thi)040:350: dam tshig chag nyams thams cad kun //
NK040(thi)040:351: bskang gyur dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK040(thi)040:352: rgyu 'byor yon gyi bdag po yis //
NK040(thi)040:353: tshe bsring dpal bskyed bsam pa sgrub //
NK040(thi)040:354: mi mthun rkyen dang bar chad sol //
NK040(thi)040:356: de nas gsang ba'i mchod pas thugs dam bskang ba ni /
NK040(thi)040:358: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK040(thi)040:359: shes rab gzugs su snang ba la //
NK040(thi)040:360: rab mdzes yid 'ong thabs kyi mchod //
NK040(thi)040:361: thabs kyi gzugs su snang ba la //
NK040(thi)040:362: shes rab nyi zlas rgyal ba mchod //
NK040(thi)040:364: lhan skyes bde stong zung 'jug las //
NK040(thi)040:365: bla ma dkon mchog thugs dam bskang //
NK040(thi)040:366: yi dam lha tshogs thugs dam bskang //
NK040(thi)040:367: rgyal ba sras bcas thugs dam ma sring mkha' 'gro'i
NK040(thi)040:368: thugs gnas gsum dpa' bo'i chos skyong srung ma'i nag
NK040(thi)040:369: po 'bum sde'i thugs las mkhan rnams kyi ma cig
NK040(thi)040:370: lha mo'i thugs ma mo bye ba'i thugs las la
NK040(thi)040:372: gtsang rigs mgon po'i thugs bstan ma skyong mdzad shugs 'gro dang //
NK040(thi)040:373: dreg pa can gyi sku gsung thugs mchog sogs /
NK040(thi)040:374: de kho na nyid kyis thugs dam bskang ba ni /
NK040(thi)040:376: gzhan yang thugs dam bskang ba ni //
NK040(thi)040:377: de ltar thugs dam bskang yul dang //
NK040(thi)040:378: rnal 'byor bskang bar byed pa dang //
NK040(thi)040:379: bskang ba yi ni cho ga dang //
NK040(thi)040:380: rten dang brten pa bcas pa dang //
NK040(thi)040:381: snang srid brten g.yo la sogs pa //
NK040(thi)040:382: kun rdzob sgyu ma rmi lam ltar //
NK040(thi)040:383: don dam chos nyid spros dang bral //
NK040(thi)040:384: skye 'gags gnas pa'i mtha' dang bral //
NK040(thi)040:385: yod min med min kun dang bral //
NK040(thi)040:386: blo yi 'dzin pa kun dang bral //
NK040(thi)040:387: mtha' bral dbu ma chen po la //
NK040(thi)040:388: ye nas bshags bya bshags byed med //
NK040(thi)040:389: rang bzhin 'od gsal lhun grub la //
NK040(thi)040:390: bskang ba ci byas ma bskang zhing //
NK040(thi)040:391: don dam chos nyid spros dang bral //
NK040(thi)040:392: kun rdzob sgyu ma lta bu yi //
NK040(thi)040:393: ngang nas bskang ba byed pa ste //
NK040(thi)040:394: gzugs kyi mchod pa khyad par 'phags //
NK040(thi)040:395: sgra yi mchod pa yid 'ong ldan //
NK040(thi)040:396: dri yi mchod pa tshim par mchod //
NK040(thi)040:397: ro yi mchod pa bde mchod ldan //
NK040(thi)040:398: reg bya'i mchod pa bla na med //
NK040(thi)040:400: bla ma dkon mchog thugs dam bskang //
NK040(thi)040:401: yi dam lha tshogs rgyal ba sras bcas ma sring
NK040(thi)040:402: mkha' 'gro'i gnas gsum dpa' bo chos skyong srung ma'i
NK040(thi)040:403: nag po 'bum sde'i ma cig lha mo'i ma mo
NK040(thi)040:404: bye ba'i thugs las la bskul gtsang rig mgon po'i
NK040(thi)040:405: brten ma skyong ma shug 'gro dang //
NK040(thi)040:406: dregs pa can gyis sku gsung thugs mchog mnyes gyur cig /
NK040(thi)040:407: rnal 'byor lam mchog sgrub pa yi //
NK040(thi)040:408: rtsa ba dang ni yan lag gis //
NK040(thi)040:409: dam tshig nyams chags gyur pa rnams //
NK040(thi)040:410: bskang gyur dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK040(thi)040:411: rgyu 'byor yon gyis bdag po yi //
NK040(thi)040:412: tshe bsring dpal bskyed bsam pa bsgrub //
NK040(thi)040:413: mi mthun rkyen dang bar chad sol //
NK040(thi)040:416: bskang ba med de bden gnyis ngang du bskang //
NK040(thi)040:417: bshags bya med de bden gnyis ngang du bshags //
NK040(thi)040:418: bzlog bya med de bden gnyis ngang du bzlog /
NK040(thi)040:419: mkha' 'gro'i thun dang phur zor bzlog /
NK040(thi)040:420: he ru ka yi gzi brjid bzlog /
NK040(thi)040:421: stobs po che yi zir gnon lha rnams kun gyi rtsub rigs bzlog /
NK040(thi)040:422: lha mi rnams kyi dmag sna gza' chen rnams kyi
NK040(thi)040:423: gdug zer gshin rje pho mo'i 'khrul 'khor bdud dmag
NK040(thi)040:425: ma mo rnams kyi khrag nad bzlog /
NK040(thi)040:426: klu'i byad du bcug pa the'u rang sri la rku
NK040(thi)040:427: ba gnod sbyin rnams kyi gzer nad btsan gyi rgyu
NK040(thi)040:429: rgyal po'i smyo 'bog gtong ba bzlog /
NK040(thi)040:430: 'byung po'i yi dwags rims nad bzlog /
NK040(thi)040:432: sngags pa'i phur zor 'phen pa bzlog /
NK040(thi)040:433: bon po'i bsdig zor 'phen pa bzlog /
NK040(thi)040:434: skyes pa'i mda' zor 'phen pa bzlog /
NK040(thi)040:435: bud med dmod zor 'phen pa bzlog /
NK040(thi)040:436: slad kyi gshed bzhi mchis pa bzlog /
NK040(thi)040:437: mo rtsis ngan pa thams cad bzlog /
NK040(thi)040:438: de la sogs pa'i gdug sems rnams //
NK040(thi)040:439: thams cad sdang ba'i dgra la b+h+yoh thams cad rbod stong steng du b+h+yoh badz+ra d+ha k+ki ni /
NK040(thi)040:440: dgra bgegs byed ma rbod stong ma ra ya b+h+yo b+h+yoh bzlog bzlog /
NK040(thi)040:442: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro 'khor bcas la //
NK040(thi)040:443: phyi nang gsang ba de kho nas //
NK040(thi)040:444: mchod cing thugs dam bskang ba ni //
NK040(thi)040:445: don gnyer rnams kyis bskul ba'i ngor //
NK040(thi)040:446: bzang gi sa mdor kun dgas sbyar //
NK040(thi)040:447: gnong ba bzod pa mdzad dge bas //
NK040(thi)040:448: ma gyur 'gro ba ma lus pas //
NK040(thi)040:449: rdo rje 'chang dbang thob par shog ///
